WEBVTT

00:00.031 --> 00:01.660
<i>Hi, I'm Chuck.</i>
<i>Here are a few things that</i>

00:01.685 --> 00:02.569
<i>you might need to know.</i>

00:02.570 --> 00:04.712
I'll be locked in solitary
the rest of my life,

00:05.080 --> 00:07.515
but one thing's going to
keep me warm at night.

00:07.550 --> 00:09.083
Do you remember Hungary?

00:09.118 --> 00:12.687
Does Chuck know
about the baby?

00:16.292 --> 00:18.243
Hey, honey,

00:18.294 --> 00:20.278
I haven't heard
from you for a while.

00:20.312 --> 00:21.546
I miss you.

00:21.580 --> 00:25.866
Wherever you are,
I hope you're okay, safe.

00:25.884 --> 00:27.168
I want you to know,

00:27.202 --> 00:31.606
if you ever feel like you need
a place to come home to,

00:31.640 --> 00:35.109
well, you have one.

00:38.647 --> 00:40.047
Who was that?

00:40.065 --> 00:41.349
Nobody.

00:41.383 --> 00:42.984
Are we a go?

00:43.018 --> 00:45.687
Affirmative.

